item.title: 【Requests】[REQ AUD] - A*M*E - Sampler (City Lights, Play the Game Boy, etc.) LOSSLESS?
item.description:
Hi all. Wondering if anyone has A*M*E's original sampler from 2012 on CD that they might be able to rip in lossless format? Don't care if it's WAV, FLAC, etc., just want to have 'City Lights' in CD quality.

It's this release: https://www.discogs.com/release/4175333-AME-Sampler
1. City Lights
2. Ride or Die
3. Play the Game Boy
4. Heartless

'City Lights' was produced by MNEK before he hit it big. Such a shame we didn't get an album from her...

Thanks in advance!
item.author: anthonyv8
